-- GM Plans to Keep Opel Factories Open Through 2014, Bild Reports
-- B y   N a o m i   K r e s g e
-- 2012-03-24T12:40:34Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-03-24/gm-plans-to-keep-opel-factories-open-through-2014-bild-reports.html
General Motors Co. (GM)  plans to keep
its Adam Opel GmbH plants open through 2014,  Bild  cited GM
Europe President Karl-Friedrich Stracke as saying in an
interview.  The automaker will seek other ways to increase its
competitiveness, including reviewing wages, the newspaper cited
Stracke as saying.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Naomi Kresge in Berlin at 
 nkresge@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Phil Serafino at 
 pserafino@bloomberg.net  